properties.title: Usage Instructions
properties.description:
Use this URL with the following arguments:lat = your latitude in decimal format, South is negative.
		lon = your longitude in decimal format, West is negative.
		radius = your search radius in nautical miles (100 is the default).
		Example: http://www.ndbc.noaa.gov/rss/ndbc_obs_search.php?lat=25.5&lon=-90.1&radius=200
